deal_general_information.query:
For the agreement named Hewlett Packar Financial Agreement, extract the following:
Name: Deal/Loan General Information
The main items for the high-level information about loan details are the parties that are involved in the credit agreement along with the signing date, loan amount, and all other parties involved like Banks and agents.
This section includes the following:
- Borrower Name
- Commitment Amount (Minimum and Maximum)
- Signing Date
- Purpose
- Parties involved (Banks, agents, etc.)

pricing_grid_information.query:
For the agreement named Hewlett Packard Financial Agreement, extract the following:
Name: Pricing Grid Information
The pricing grid is usually the information of the interest applicable to the borrower. The interest rate applicable is tied to the financial covenants ratio. If the ratio level is maintained according to the table of the pricing grid then the applicable interest rate will be different.
This section includes the following:
- Split Rated?
- Split By > 1 Lev?
- Performance Types - Performance Price Code
- Performance Types - Column Number
- Grid - Min Op
- Grid - xyz Min
- Grid - Max Op
- Grid - xyz Max
- Base Rates
- Fees
